<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NutriTrack - Error de Activación</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 3px solid #e74c3c;
        }
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo img {
            width: 100px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .logo h1 {
            color: #6ab04c;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin: 15px 0 0 0;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);
        }
        .main-title {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .error-details {
            background-color: #ffeaa7;
            border: 2px solid #fdcb6e;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #856404;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .error-details h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #856404;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .description {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .solutions {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 2px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .solutions h3 {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .solutions ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .solutions li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #856404;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .solutions li::before {
            content: '💡';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 14px 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #6ab04c;
            color: white;
            border-color: #6ab04c;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #5a9d3e;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(106, 176, 76, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #6ab04c;
            border-color: #6ab04c;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #6ab04c;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .contact-info h3 {
            color: #6ab04c;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .contact-info p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            color: #2d5016;
        }
        .contact-info a {
            color: #6ab04c;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .contact-info a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        /* Responsive design */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 25px;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }
            .main-title {
                font-size: 26px;
            }
            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 250px;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="../../assets/logo.png" alt="NutriTrack Logo">
            <h1>nutritrack</h1>
        </div>
        

        
        <h1 class="main-title">Error de Activación</h1>
        
        <p class="error-message">
            <%= error || 'No pudimos activar tu cuenta' %>
        </p>
        
        <% if (locals.errorDetails) { %>
            <div class="error-details">
                <h4>Detalles del error:</h4>
                <p><%= errorDetails %></p>
                <% if (locals.errorType) { %>
                    <div class="error-code">Código: <%= errorType %></div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="description">
            <p>El enlace de activación ha expirado, no es válido o ya ha sido utilizado anteriormente.</p>
        </div>


        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>¿Primera vez en NutriTrack?</strong></p>
            <p>Regístrate fácilmente y comienza a controlar tu alimentación de forma inteligente.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <em>Gracias por tu interés en NutriTrack.</em>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function tryLogin() {
            // Redirigir a la página de login
            window.location.href = '/auth/login';
        }

        function registerAgain() {
            // Redirigir a la página de registro
            window.location.href = '/auth/register';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>